    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The engine has significant performance issues and the transmission requires a full overhaul to be functional. Externally, there is noticeable rust and several body panels have deep dents, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear on the upholstery. It is not currently in roadworthy condition and will require professional mechanical attention.",
